---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PosterGallery from '../../components/PosterGallery.astro';

// Static page generated automatically from HTML
---
<BaseLayout
  title="MASSKA · International Theatre Review"
  description="XXIV MASSKA International Theatre Review 2025. Theatre performances November 16-20 in Sopot. Performances also available online."
  lang="en"
  showPartners={true}
  redirectToPreferredLanguage={false}
>
<section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <!--  <p class="eyebrow">XXIV International Theatre Review</p> -->
                <h1>MASSKA 2025 — International Theatre Review</h1>
                <p>Discover exceptional theatre performances. The
                    festival takes place in Sopot, November 16–20, 2025. Performances also available online.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a class="button primary" href="program.html">View schedule</a>
                    <a class="button secondary" href="online.html">Watch online</a>
                </div>
                <div class="chip-row" role="list">
                    <span class="chip" role="listitem">November 16–20, 2025</span>
                    <span class="chip" role="listitem">Sopot, Poland</span>
                    <span class="chip" role="listitem">Available online</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <figure class="hero-media">
                <img src="../assets/img/head.webp" alt="MASSKA festival header graphic" decoding="async"
                    fetchpriority="high">
            </figure>
        </section>

        <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="introduction">
            <div class="section-inner">
                <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 2rem;">
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
                        <div style="width: min(380px, 100%);">
                            <div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 420px; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 0.75rem; background: #f5f7fb;">
                                <iframe style="position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0;"
                                    src="https://zrzutka.pl/bax8c7/widget/13" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" title="Donation drive"></iframe>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h2 id="introduction">Opening Words</h2>
                <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <p>Sometimes I wonder how much you can receive from theatre. Not from the stage, spotlights, or
                        applause... but from the process itself – from people, from encounters, from being together. I
                        find the answer when I look at our actors – people who bring their stories, emotions, and
                        sensitivity to the stage – I see tremendous strength in them. In theatre, it's not about
                        perfection, but about authenticity. And that's what theatre gives: a reminder that each of us
                        has value, that everyone has something to say.</p>

                    <p>For me, theatre is a place where everything becomes possible – where what is difficult, fragile,
                        imperfect, gains a voice. It's a space where a person can be themselves, without masks, though
                        paradoxically we often use masks.</p>

                    <p><strong>And Masska…</strong></p>

                    <p>Masska is more than a festival to me. It's a meeting of hearts. I know many of you think this way
                        and I thank you for every such confession. It's a time when different worlds, different bodies,
                        different languages connect in one common rhythm. It's proof that theatre can be a bridge –
                        between people, between ways of seeing the world, between what is "ours" and "other".</p>

                    <p>When I look at what happens during Masska – how much joy, tenderness, courage there is...</p>

                    <p><em>Masska reminds me why I do theatre.</em></p>

                    <p>It's the same here, online, despite the hundreds of thousands of kilometers that often separate
                        us. Created for pandemic times, Masska online has become an integral part of the festival.
                        Thanks to our website, we can present performances by theatre ensembles. This year our
                        website has been reconstructed for the festival,
                        which takes place offline.</p>

                    <p>We really want to connect all our festival forms even more.</p>

                    <p><em>Masska reminds me why I do theatre.</em></p>

                    <p>To awaken. To connect. To preserve what is real in people. As best I can. So Masska, endure,
                        wherever you are. You're ready for this.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="promotional-video">
            <div class="section-inner">
                <h2 id="promotional-video">MASSKA 2025 Promotional Video</h2>
                <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Watch the preview of this year's festival edition
                </p>
                <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
                        <iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" width="560"
                            height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RbvAPtKZB9s?si=zcfzelvvXuj1WoMQ"
                            title="MASSKA 2025 - Promotional video" frameborder="0"
                            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                            referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen>
                        </iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="page-section alt" aria-labelledby="festival-schedule">
            <div class="section-inner two-column">
                <div>
                    <h2 id="festival-schedule">Festival Schedule</h2>
                    <div class="timeline">
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <h3>November 16–20, 2025 · In-Person Festival</h3>
                            <p>Live performances at three venues in Sopot: Mamuszki 14, Teatr Atelier, and Wybrzeże
                                Theatre
                                Chamber Stage. Workshops, meetings with creators, and evening events.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <h3>MASSKA Online</h3>
                            <p>Selected performances available online with Polish and English subtitles. Downloadable
                                materials and performance descriptions for audiences worldwide.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <h3>Hybrid Format</h3>
                            <p>Once again, we're combining the live festival experience with the global accessibility of
                                our
                                online platform, so theatre groups can reach the widest possible audience.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <aside class="info-panel" aria-label="Key festival information">
                    <h2>Key information</h2>
                    <dl>
                        <div>
                            <dt>Edition</dt>
                            <dd>XXIV International Review</dd>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <dt>Dates</dt>
                            <dd>November 16–20, 2025</dd>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <dt>Format</dt>
                            <dd>Hybrid · Live in Sopot and globally online</dd>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <dt>Participants</dt>
                            <dd>Theatre ensembles</dd>
                        </div>
                    </dl>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="page-section alt" aria-labelledby="highlights-section">
            <div class="section-inner">
                <h2 id="highlights-section">What the festival offers</h2>
                <div class="card-grid">
                    <article class="card">
                        <h3>Live performances</h3>
                        <p>Over 20 performances by theatre ensembles at three venues in Sopot.
                        </p>
                        <a class="button ghost" href="program.html">View schedule</a>
                    </article>
                    <article class="card">
                        <h3>Online streaming</h3>
                        <p>Selected performances available online with subtitles in two
                            languages.</p>
                        <a class="button ghost" href="online.html">Online platform</a>
                    </article>
                    <article class="card">
                        <h3>Workshops and meetings</h3>
                        <p>Dance, theatre, and music workshops led by professionals. Meetings with performance creators.
                        </p>
                        <a class="button ghost" href="program.html#detailed-program">Details</a>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <PosterGallery lang="en" />
</BaseLayout>
